      <title>红海沉船正在进水等待救援</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-15/stricken-red-sea-ship-is-taking-on-water-as-it-awaits-salvage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一艘在红海被无人机撞击后被遗弃的船只正在慢慢进水，两艘船只正在前往救援的途中。]]></description>
