    <item>
      <title>全球经济图表：美联储维持利率不变；日本央行放弃日元风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-15/world-economy-latest-federal-reserve-holds-bank-of-japan-leaves-yen-at-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储官员预计今年仅会降息一次，并预测2025年还会进一步降息，这强化了政策制定者的呼吁，即维持借贷成本更长时间的高位以抑制通胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-15/world-economy-latest-federal-reserve-holds-bank-of-japan-leaves-yen-at-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 15 Jun 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
