      <title>乌克兰下周将因维修而面临更长的停电时间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-15/ukraine-blackouts-to-expand-next-week-due-to-repairs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰电网负责人预计，随着饱受战争摧残的国家继续面临电力短缺问题，已经持续很长时间的停电还将进一步扩大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-15/ukraine-blackouts-to-expand-next-week-due-to-repairs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 15 Jun 2024 06:49:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
